lead_paragraph: With two on and two out in the third inning, Miguel Cabrera struck out swinging at a pitch that was low and inside, and the slugger was so off balance he ended up on one knee.

headline.print_headline: Tigers Homer 3 Times in 7-Run 5th, Beat Marlins 7-5
